<h2>Schedule update</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @patient.first_name %>,</p>

<p><%= @provider.display_name %> is running approximately <strong><%= @delay_minutes %> minutes</strong> behind schedule.</p>

<p>Your updated appointment time is <strong><%= @new_time %></strong>.</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">We apologize for the inconvenience. If you need to reschedule, please reply to this email or contact the practice.</p>

<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 24px;">— <%= @tenant.name %> via Schedulite</p>
